## Appendix A: Glossary

**Chronos:** Linear, predictable time; clock time  
**Kairos:** Opportune moment; temporal inflection point  
**Pace:** Rate of change in narrative momentum  
**Metastability:** State of maximum sensitivity to perturbation  
**Narrative Tension:** Accumulated story pressure before release  
**I-Vector:** Calibrated intuition coefficient  
**Variance Bloom:** Rapid expansion of outcome probability distribution

